And my captain

9
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,900
was wise and firm,

10
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:10,150
like the North Star,

11
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:11,670
guiding us

12
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,000
