13
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,910
So, on behalf of

14
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:17,510
Oceanvision International Logistics Group,

15
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:19,470
I have decided to

16
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:22,320
name this scholarship after Xinghan.

17
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,079
I believe

18
00:02:25,850 --> 00:02:27,810
every student present here

19
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:31,520
can be like the daughter
of the Xinghan's captain,

20
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:32,630
who is also

21
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:35,970
one of the committee members
of the Xinghan Scholarship,

22
00:02:35,970 --> 00:02:37,090
[Xinghan Sets Sail,
Building Dreams Together]

23
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:38,030
your Ms. Yan Ling,

24
00:02:37,110 --> 00:02:37,700
[Xinghan Scholarship Donation Ceremony]

25
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:39,930
braving the waves

26
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:44,240
to finally reach your ideal shore.

27
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,840
Xinghan Scholarship?

28
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,150
At the donation ceremony,

29
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:54,030
Yan Ling is in the center.

30
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:54,960
What?

31
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:56,430
Look.

32
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:58,780
[Xinghan Scholarship Donation Ceremony]

33
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:02,360
Is their boss called Ding Zhibo?

34
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:03,680
How did you know?

35
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,700
Do you know him?

36
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:05,960
How could I not?

37
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:09,120
He's such a famous entrepreneur.

38
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,100
I've known about him since college.

39
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:26,790
Ms. Yan.

40
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,430
Ms. Yan.

41
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:36,850
Yan Ling.

42
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,120
Yan Ling, I'll send you home.

43
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,750
Yan Ling!

44
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,600
The most important part of the third step,
the Lure Trap,

45
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,870
is the takedown you've been waiting for!

46
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,659
That will be

47
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,390
tonight!

48
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,070
With the virtual identity of

49
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:00,560
the racing driver Murong Baichuan,

50
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,830
Xuan added 128 girls on WeChat,

51
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,950
chatted with 52 of them,

52
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,480
with an exchange of more than 10 messages.

53
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,180
Your mission tonight is

54
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,680
to help Xuan
take down the girl he asked out,

55
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,390
to draw first blood!

56
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,160
Alright!

57
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,120
Thank you, thank you.

58
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,810
Introduce yourselves!

59
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,360
I am

60
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,210
Murong's buddy,

61
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,030
Night God,

62
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,040
and I'm also a racing driver.

63
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,330
[Night God, Racing Driver]

64
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:22,800
I am a director!

65
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,730
I want to use Murong as a prototype

66
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:25,870
to make a movie.

67
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:27,210
[Ouyang, Director]

68
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,000
I am

69
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:29,430
the nutritionist

70
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,270
of Murong's team!

71
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,190
[Kevin, Nutritionist]

72
00:05:32,260 --> 00:05:32,940
I am

73
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,510
Murong's stylist,

74
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,390
Wenwen!

75
00:05:35,409 --> 00:05:37,770
[Wenwen, Stylist]

76
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,480
I am,

77
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:39,600
um,

78
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,750
Murong's att...

79
00:05:40,610 --> 00:05:43,640
[Qiang, Attorney]

80
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,600
attorney!

81
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:45,010
What do you want to say?

82
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,640
Murong Baichuan,

83
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,900
Night God;

84
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:51,270
aren't the names too fake?

85
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:55,120
Do you know why telephone scammers

86
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,380
always have an accent?

87
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,950
Those who become alert
when they hear dialects

88
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:01,560
are less likely to be fooled!

89
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,720
It is to screen out the smarter ones!

90
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,320
With such a dramatic script,

91
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,430
the girls who believe it

92
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,560
are much easier to take down!

93
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,310
You are so wise!

94
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:12,360
Right.

95
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,170
Ms. Wenwen here

96
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,420
is our wingman.

97
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,700
With a girl around,

98
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,270
it's more likely that they will

99
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,470
let their guard down.

100
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:20,380
Xuan said

101
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,720
this girl

102
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,120
isn't very experienced.

103
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,030
She will

104
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,550
probably bring a friend.

105
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:27,070
They're here.

106
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,680
Hello, hello!

107
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,320
Xiaoyi,

108
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:31,950
right?

109
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:33,290
Here. Sit here.

110
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:33,950
First,

111
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,430
isolate the target.

112
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,870
Cut her off from everything
that's giving her a sense of security

113
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,330
so she can only rely on you.

114
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,000
I find you really pretty.

115
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,580
Second,

116
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:43,080
confuse the target.

117
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,380
Hit on her friend

118
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:46,700
to make her feel unattractive

119
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,450
and ignored.

120
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,750
Welcome!

121
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:49,750
-Cheers!
-Third,

122
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,390
remember the notion of an alpha male

123
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:52,590
that I told you about?

124
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:53,670
Today,

125
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,750
Xuan is the center of attention,

126
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:56,890
the alpha among us.

127
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:57,770
As his buddies,

128
00:06:57,770 --> 00:06:59,000
-we must sing his praises.
-Murong!

129
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,040
Here's a toast to you!

130
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,240
I wouldn't be where I am today
without you.

131
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:02,950
Murong,

132
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:05,070
thank you for the job opportunity!

133
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:05,730
Murong,

134
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,390
thank you for the promotion!

135
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:09,070
I hope Mr. Murong can star

136
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,070
as the leading man

137
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,190
in my movie!

138
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:13,040
Let's all help each other out, OK?

139
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,390
OK!

140
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:15,310
Elevate him and belittle her.

141
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,680
Now, all the elevated one needs to do

142
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,750
to the belittled one is

143
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,880
to give her the slightest validation.

144
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,360
Don't you think

145
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:24,070
a girl like Xiaoyi

146
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:25,240
is the real catch?

147
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,240
Right!

148
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,120
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

149
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,000
One look and I know
she's beautiful and kind.

150
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,390
Exceptionally elegant.

151
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:30,950
Fourth,

152
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:33,960
we finally reach the most important part:

153
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,360
push the boundaries.

154
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,480
Murong,

155
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,159
you are being too much of a gentleman!

156
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,810
The girl is going all out.

157
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:50,240
What are you waiting for?

158
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,100
Exactly.

159
00:07:51,130 --> 00:07:51,820
Hurry!

160
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,680
Come on!

161
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,600
Tear it!

162
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,240
Come on!

163
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,220
Tear it now!

164
00:08:07,330 --> 00:08:10,490
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

165
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,750
You're awake.

166
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:15,880
What happened to me?

167
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,560
Why am I here?

168
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,750
You drove home in the rain

169
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:20,800
and got a high fever.

170
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,800
You scared Jiale.

171
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:26,630
W-Where...

172
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:27,510
Where is Jiale?

173
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,580
He's at home. Don't worry.

174
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,600
I ordered delivery food for him.

175
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,659
He saw you were sick

176
00:08:33,289 --> 00:08:34,510
and remembered I'm a doctor,

177
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,480
so he called me.

178
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:38,150
I'm so sorry

179
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,080
to trouble you again.

180
00:08:40,909 --> 00:08:41,840
It's no trouble.

181
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:43,480
Here.

182
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:50,620
Jiale said

183
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,610
you had an argument with your mom,

184
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,160
and it seemed serious.

185
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,840
He's very worried about you.

186
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,570
He said his grandma

187
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,360
is also a teacher,

188
00:09:06,030 --> 00:09:07,560
and she sounds very strict.

189
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,440
She is also alone.

190
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,790
Usually, such people

191
00:09:14,650 --> 00:09:15,780
have high standards

192
00:09:16,070 --> 00:09:17,530
and are very controlling.

193
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:22,100
It's not what you think.

194
00:09:26,810 --> 00:09:28,070
Actually, many people

195
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:32,190
have difficulty managing
their relationships with their parents.

196
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,000
For women,

197
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:37,080
a mother's influence
is especially profound.

198
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,590
Many girls

199
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:41,450
want to escape their mothers' influence.

200
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,450
But they somehow always

201
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:46,280
end up living just like their mothers.

202
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:48,310
Just like you,

203
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,740
you became a single mom

204
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,670
just like your mother.

205
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,570
The process of cutting the umbilical cord

206
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,720
is very difficult.

207
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,080
Sometimes it's even bloody.

208
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,930
You must never feel

209
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,830
that you are terrible

210
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,150
or selfish.

211
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,390
The fact is you don't owe anyone anything.

212
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:14,360
I owe my mom a lot.

213
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,680
My dad's accident...

214
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,480
was caused by me.

215
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:40,910
Why isn't your dad back yet?

216
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:42,840
The food is getting cold.

217
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:45,320
How about I page him?

218
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:47,120
How can he check it while riding?

219
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,960
It's all because of you.

220
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,150
Aren't the cakes from the bakery

221
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,480
at the gate good enough?

222
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,540
You had to make him go so far to buy one.

223
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,630
My dad said

224
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:55,610
only that bakery uses real cream.

225
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,790
Again with the "my dad."

226
00:10:57,790 --> 00:10:59,280
He just spoils you rotten.

227
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,240
Must be my dad!

228
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:02,730
It must be your dad.

229
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,320
Hello, where are you?

230
00:11:09,220 --> 00:11:10,750
Yes, speaking. Who is this?

231
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:31,670
Dad...

232
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:34,790
Dad...

233
00:11:38,830 --> 00:11:39,830
Don't ever forget

234
00:11:40,610 --> 00:11:42,770
that your father died because of you.

235
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:45,280
Dad...

236
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:06,450
Cry it out.

237
00:12:08,090 --> 00:12:09,150
Don't hold it back.

238
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:11,890
I feel like you've been

239
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:13,510
holding it in for a long time.

240
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,500
It's going to be OK.

241
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,430
Everything will be OK, Yan Ling.

242
00:12:23,970 --> 00:12:25,130
Now I know why

243
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:28,020
you reacted that way to the cake

244
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:31,510
when we had a meal last time.

245
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,390
Since then,

246
00:12:37,770 --> 00:12:39,830
I stopped celebrating my birthdays.

247
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:53,250
Don't punish yourself like this.

248
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,450
Actually, your mom must know deep down

249
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,580
that it wasn't your fault.

250
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,330
It was an accident.

251
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,220
You can't let guilt bind you

252
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:06,620
for the rest of your life.

253
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:09,120
But I could never

254
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:13,370
make up for such a mistake.

255
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:21,030
So in your mind,

256
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,320
mistakes are unforgivable.

257
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,160
Just like how you treated Jiale before.

258
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,860
No matter how big the mistake,

259
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,810
I believe

260
00:13:48,910 --> 00:13:50,170
you have atoned for it.

261
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,730
You don't need to hear

262
00:13:58,560 --> 00:13:59,890
any criticism

263
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,390
from anyone anymore.

264
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,640
It is Jiale's dad.

265
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:41,960
Answer it.

266
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,510
Hello?

267
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,500
Y-Yan Ling.

268
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:49,280
Listen to me.

269
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:51,200
Take Jiale right now

270
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:53,200
to the lobby of his tutoring center.

271
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:55,600
J-Just say I dropped him off
for his Math Olympiad class

272
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:58,050
and y-you're picking him up.

273
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,150
N-No, no.

274
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,120
Don't ask why right now.

275
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,890
I don't have time to explain.

276
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,550
Don't forget to bring his backpack.

277
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:05,320
Also, bring me a T-shirt

278
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:07,010
a-a-and a pair of slippers.

279
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,450
A-And also a hat!

280
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,630
H-Hurry up.

281
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:13,330
I'll wait for you downstairs.

282
00:15:14,460 --> 00:15:15,600
OK, I got it.

283
00:15:15,130 --> 00:15:17,650
[Nursing Rounds and Consultation System]

284
00:15:23,810 --> 00:15:27,130
[Emergency]

285
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,960
You sure you don't need me to take you?

286
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,440
No need.

287
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:38,910
I don't have many clothes in my duty room.

288
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:39,570
Just these.

289
00:15:40,830 --> 00:15:42,560
I've left the medicine inside.

290
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,120
Don't forget to take it.

291
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,000
OK.

292
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,000
[Emergency]

